snippet.description:
Our beloved foodies Jason Day and Ben An got together to play a game of guessing the ingredients of bibigo mandu. 
Mandu lover Ben was so confident to win this game...but guess what? 
Jason loved eating mandu as much as Ben and came from behind to beat this game!

Did you all know that there are all kinds of ingredient full of flavors in mandu? You might be able to guess more than Ben and Jason once you try!
